{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>House Builder 2: Craft Your Dream Home</strong></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2827960/extras/House_Builder_2_616.gif?t=1734727708\" /><br>In House Builder 2 you build your dream constructions with friends or alone in a vibrant, low-poly open world! Buy materials for work, load it up, and drive to your next job in the ultimate co-op construction adventure!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>MAIN FEATURES</strong></h2>\ud83d\udee0\ufe0f <strong>PREPARING FOR WORK</strong><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2827960/extras/Preparation_616.gif?t=1734727708\" /><br>Gear up and get ready\u2014every job starts with the right tools and a plan! Firstly, you need to look what you need for your next construction. Go to the local warehouse, buy it, and load it on the truck.<br><br>\ud83d\ude9a <strong>GETTING TO WORK</strong><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2827960/extras/Getting_to_work_616.gif?t=1734727708\" /><br>Don\u2019t be late or you can miss your ride. Load up, hit the road, and make sure everything gets delivered. On-site, before the job, you must unload all the stuff needed for the construction.<br><br>\ud83d\udc77\u200d\u2642\ufe0f\ud83d\udc77\u200d\u2640\ufe0f  <strong>CO-OP MODE</strong><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2827960/extras/Coop_Building_616.gif?t=1734727708\" /><br>Building a dream home is more fun with friends! Team up with fellow builders in our new co-op mode, where you can collaborate on projects, share resources, and design together. Whether you're constructing a cozy cottage or a majestic mansion, teamwork makes the dream work!<br><br>\ud83c\udfe1 <strong>SOLO BUILDING</strong><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2827960/extras/Builiding_Solo_616.gif?t=1734727708\" /><br>Prefer peace and quiet? Take your time, unwind, and complete every challenge solo.<br><br>\ud83c\udf0d <strong>TRUE OPEN WORLD</strong><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2827960/extras/Open_World_616.gif?t=1734727708\" /><br>Unleash your creativity in a sprawling open world teeming with possibilities. Explore it, find the place you want to work, and begin your job. The vast landscape is your canvas \u2013 shape it to your liking!<br><br>\ud83d\udd28 <strong>ADVANCED BUILDING MECHANICS</strong><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2827960/extras/Buildings_616.gif?t=1734727708\" /><br>Experience the next level of building simulation with advanced mechanics that offer more precision and control. Utilize a wide range of tools and materials to construct homes that are aesthetically pleasing and structurally sound. Take on challenging missions, complete building contracts, and unlock new tools and upgrades as you progress. House Builder 2 offers a dynamic gameplay experience that keeps you engaged and motivated to build and explore.<br><br>\ud83c\udf08 <strong>STUNNING COLORFUL GRAPHICS</strong><br>Dive into a visually captivating world where rich and vibrant colors bring every detail to life. House Builder 2 offers a feast for the eyes, from the lush landscapes to the intricate interiors, ensuring every building project feels unique and beautiful.<br><br>Get ready to embark on the building adventure of a lifetime with House Builder 2. Whether you're a seasoned architect or a novice builder, there's something here for everyone. Grab your tools and start crafting your dream home today!","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2827960?t=1734727708","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2827960/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1734727708","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2827960/15b76427f5bbe7052efcf3029e34e58ae00f13bc/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1734727708","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2827960/15b76427f5bbe7052efcf3029e34e58ae00f13bc/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1734727708","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen Co-op","id":39},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen","id":24},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Remote Play Together","id":44}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>House Builder 2: Craft Your Dream Home</strong></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2827960/extras/House_Builder_2_616.gif?t=1734727708\" /><br>In House Builder 2 you build your dream constructions with friends or alone in a vibrant, low-poly open world! Buy materials for work, load it up, and drive to your next job in the ultimate co-op construction adventure!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>MAIN FEATURES</strong></h2>\ud83d\udee0\ufe0f <strong>PREPARING FOR WORK</strong><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2827960/extras/Preparation_616.gif?t=1734727708\" /><br>Gear up and get ready\u2014every job starts with the right tools and a plan! Firstly, you need to look what you need for your next construction. Go to the local warehouse, buy it, and load it on the truck.<br><br>\ud83d\ude9a <strong>GETTING TO WORK</strong><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2827960/extras/Getting_to_work_616.gif?t=1734