House Builder 2 offers a dynamic gameplay experience that keeps you engaged and motivated to build and explore.<br><br>\ud83c\udf08 <strong>STUNNING COLORFUL GRAPHICS</strong><br>Dive into a visually captivating world where rich and vibrant colors bring every detail to life. House Builder 2 offers a feast for the eyes, from the lush landscapes to the intricate interiors, ensuring every building project feels unique and beautiful.<br><br>Get ready to embark on the building adventure of a lifetime with House Builder 2. Whether you're a seasoned architect or a novice builder, there's something here for everyone. Grab your tools and start crafting your dream home today!","developers":["FreeMind S.A."],"genres":[{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Casual","id":"4"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"Simulation","id":"28"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2827960/header.jpg?t=1734727708","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257055232,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257055232/movie480.mp4?t=1726483736","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257055232/movie_max.mp4?t=1726483736"},"name":"House Builder 2 - Announcement Trailer","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257055232/movie.293x165.jpg?t=1726483736","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257055232/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1726483736","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257055232/movie_max_vp9.webm?t=1726483736"}},{"highlight":true,"id":257083171,"mp4":{"480":"http://